I recently traveled all the way from the United States to get my root canal treatment done at Sterling Dental Clinic, Vasant Vihar, Delhi—and let me just say, it was one of the best and most reassuring decisions I’ve ever made.

@tarunkumargiroti  @priyankagiroti @thesterlingdentalclinic 

From the moment I walked into the clinic, I knew I was in exceptional hands. The atmosphere, the hygiene, the technology and the energy of the place spoke volumes about their commitment to excellence. But what truly makes this clinic stand out is the incredible team behind it.

I was treated with such care, professionalism and expertise by Dr. Shivangi , who made the entire root canal procedure feel effortless. She was calm, extremely thorough and made sure I felt safe and understood every step of the process. Her gentle yet confident approach was incredibly comforting.

A heartfelt thank you to Dr. Tarun Giroti and Dr. Priyanka Giroti, the visionary minds behind Sterling Dental Clinic. Their leadership, dedication to the highest standards and passion for patient care reflect in every corner of the clinic.

Being U.S. Embassy empaneled, Sterling Dental Clinic operates at world-class standards, providing international-level dental care that truly surpasses expectations. Their attention to detail, patient-first philosophy and cutting-edge techniques make them a global benchmark for excellence in dentistry.

I feel genuinely lucky and proud to have been treated at Sterling Dental Clinic. Whether you’re in India or anywhere across the globe—this is the place you can trust with your smile.

I highly, highly recommend Sterling Dental Clinic to anyone looking for the absolute best in dental care—whether you’re based in India or flying in from abroad like I did. You’ll be in the safest, most capable hands.

Thank you once again to the entire team for giving me such a seamless and exceptional experience!

Happy Birthday to the most beautiful person I’ve ever known and will ever know!!!! I know love is already such a meaningful word but you literally are the meaning of love to me. I know love is real because you exist and you’re so full of it. I can’t believe the girl I used to fight over the most things (and in all honesty I very much still do) is 18 😵‍💫 like can you believe it? Anwita, the girl who cries out of fear when she sees a frog, is EIGHTEEN, as in, an adult 😨 
I would say “I love you” but it really doesn’t do justice to how much you mean to me. Your name comes out of my mouth more than my own. I could probably live without oxygen, but not in any universe could I imagine life without you 🤗 okay this is too sappy i love u happy birthday aunty
